      h3 How it Works
      p You sign up.
      p We have an initial visit where we assess the size of the silver spoon in your mouth.
      p You never have to worry about feeding yourself again.
    section.pricing
      h3 Introductory Pricing
      div.three-wrapper
        div.three
          p.three-subhead Tea Spoon
          p 1-3 Meals
          p $10 per week
          p.per-month $30 per month 
            span.small (with a one year committment)
        div.three.big
          p.three-subhead Table Spoon
          p 3-6 Meals
          p $20 per week
          p.per-month $70 per month 
            span.small (with a one year committment)
        div.three
          p.three-subhead Soup Spoon
          p 6-10 Meals
          p $30 per week
          p.per-month $100 per month 
            span.small (with a one year committment)
    section.trust-and-security
      h3 Trust and Security
      blockquote 
        p.quote This team of mavericks has created a roomba for your mouth.
        p.quote-attrib -TechCrunch
      div.three-wrapper
        div.three
          p.three-subhead Background Checked
          p All of our carefully trained helpers pass strict background checks to ensure they won't put anything other than food into your mouth.
        div.three.big
          p.three-subhead Security
          p We use advances in mobile and GPS technology to keep tabs on our helpers 24/7.
        div.three
          p.three-subhead Reliable
          p All of our helpers are community rated. If they fall below 4.7 stars we give them the boot without warning.
